            {
              "h3": "Useful scoping inputs",
              "paragraph": "Share sample contacts, companies, deals, or tickets, current custom properties, pipeline rules, association labels, duplicate scenarios, and screenshots or logs of actual failures. If a specific form or lifecycle stage is involved, name it directly."
