              "h3": "Slack delivery details to capture",
              "paragraph": "Specify approved channels, private channel access requirements, message templates, mention rules, thread behavior, and whether the workflow must store the Slack message ID for later updates."
            },
            {
              "h3": "Ownership and handover",
              "paragraph": "Document who owns the workflow after launch, who can change spreadsheets or channels, what logs are required, and how future staff should troubleshoot failed messages or row updates without guesswork."
            }
          ]
        }
